featured_reviews.review_id:
It's our local masjid, so I guess I will describe it as good as it is. No doubt it's a beautiful masjid and it's single tower make it more beautiful, it's internal work and decoration is too gud and managed as well, it's outer slabstone art and garden gives  a fab look. The main thing is that this masjid has enough space, so that a couple hundred people can easily pray at once, it has ac facility too.
I think it'll become more beautiful if we start praying at least 5 time a day.
